    public abstract class AbstractControlledDataOutboundPort
extends fr.upmc.components.ports.AbstractDataOutboundPort
implements ControlledDataRequiredI.ControlledPullI
    The class AbstractControlledDataOutboundPort defines an abstract controlled outbound port where the push interface adds control method to start and stop the pushing.
